        <mxCell id="srfS4grJ1zUWjvvm8V-F-9" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Code Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Anonymous Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Droid Sans Mono&amp;quot;, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; float: none; display: inline !important;&quot;&gt;cond[0] → init_latents (B, 512, h, w)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Source Code Pro, DejaVu Sans Mono, Ubuntu Mono, Anonymous Pro, Droid Sans Mono, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace, PingFang SC, Microsoft YaHei, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; white-space: pre; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);&quot;&gt;融合焦距堆栈特征(通过不确定性+门控融合)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="350" x="980" y="1607.34" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="srfS4grJ1zUWjvvm8V-F-11" edge="1" parent="1" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;rounded=0;" value="">
          <mxGeometry height="50" relative="1" width="50" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="970" y="1580" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="970" y="2430" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="srfS4grJ1zUWjvvm8V-F-13" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), rgba(237, 237, 237, 0.05)); color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237)); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Code Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Anonymous Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Droid Sans Mono&amp;quot;, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;  ▼ ═══ 渐进上采样 (3 级, mult=2) ═══&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Code Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Anonymous Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Droid Sans Mono&amp;quot;, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; float: none; display: inline !important;&quot;&gt;  │&lt;br&gt;  │  级 0: (B, 512, h, w)&lt;br&gt;  │     init_latents + ConvTranspose2d(512→512, k=1, s=1)(cond[1])&lt;br&gt;  │    → ResUpsampleBil(512→512, depth=2): Conv3×3+BN+ReLU ×2 + bilinear×2&lt;br&gt;  │    → out[0] (B, 512, 2h, 2w) ≈ (B, 512, 68, 90)&lt;br&gt;  │&lt;br&gt;  │  级 1: (B, 512, 2h, 2w)&lt;br&gt;  │    + ConvTranspose2d(512→512, k=2, s=2)(cond[2])&lt;br&gt;  │    → ResUpsampleBil(512→256, depth=2)&lt;br&gt;  │    → out[1] (B, 256, 4h, 4w) ≈ (B, 256, 136, 180)&lt;br&gt;  │&lt;br&gt;  │  级 2: (B, 256, 4h, 4w)&lt;br&gt;  │    + ConvTranspose2d(512→256, k=4, s=4)(cond[3])&lt;br&gt;  │    → ResUpsampleBil(256→128, depth=2)&lt;br&gt;  │    → out[2] (B, 128, 8h, 8w) ≈ (B, 128, 272, 360)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="90" width="330" x="950" y="1682.34" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="srfS4grJ1zUWjvvm8V-F-14" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Code Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Anonymous Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Droid Sans Mono&amp;quot;, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;对 out_features[0,1,2] 每级各一个 FocalContextBridge:&#xa;  │&#xa;  ├─ 级0: FocalContextBridge(512, 512)  → out[0] × (1 + gate₀·σ(fs₀))&#xa;  ├─ 级1: FocalContextBridge(512, 256)  → out[1] × (1 + gate₁·σ(fs₁))&#xa;  └─ 级2: FocalContextBridge(512, 128)  → out[2] × (1 + gate₂·σ(fs₂))&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="360" x="975" y="1975" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="srfS4grJ1zUWjvvm8V-F-15" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Code Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Anonymous Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Droid Sans Mono&amp;quot;, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; float: none; display: inline !important;&quot;&gt;BinsHead(采用log分布)没有使用adabins等动态分布&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="190" x="970" y="2105" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="srfS4grJ1zUWjvvm8V-F-16" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=0" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Code Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Anonymous Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Droid Sans Mono&amp;quot;, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; float: none; display: inline !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;RefineModule(动态微调)使用confidence来调节搜索带宽，不确定性越大的部分搜索带宽越大&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="420" x="970" y="2165" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="srfS4grJ1zUWjvvm8V-F-17" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Code Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Anonymous Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Droid Sans Mono&amp;quot;, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;depth&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="40" width="80" x="970" y="2235" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <UserObject label="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Code Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Anonymous Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Droid Sans Mono&amp;quot;, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; float: none; display: inline !important;&quot;&gt;═══ 优化损失 (losses[&quot;opt&quot;]) ═══&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. SILog (主深度损失):&lt;br&gt;   d = log(pred_depth) - log(gt_depth)&lt;br&gt;   SILog = mean(d²) - λ × mean(d)²        权重: config&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;2. depth_pre_auto:&lt;br&gt;   BinsHead 粗深度 × rays_z vs GT          权重: 0.5 × SILog.weight&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;3. depth_post_auto:&lt;br&gt;   RefineModule 精深度 × rays_z vs GT      权重: 1.0 × SILog.weight&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;4. dff_aux_depth:&lt;br&gt;   exp(dff_logdepth_aux) → 下采样GT比较     权重: 0.3 × SILog.weight&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;5. EdgeGuidedLocalSSI:&lt;br&gt;   边缘引导局部尺度-位移不变性损失            权重: config&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;6. Regression:&lt;br&gt;   L1 距离                                  权重: config&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;7. Confidence_conf:&lt;br&gt;   -log(confidence) × |depth_error|          权重: config&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 153, 153);&quot;&gt;8. teacher_camera:&lt;br&gt;   teacher_rays vs GT rays                  权重: camera.weight&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;9. distill_rays:&lt;br&gt;   warmup × 0.5 × (1 - cos(student, teacher))  权重: 渐进&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;10. distill_intrinsics:&lt;br&gt;    warmup × 0.1 × MSE(student_K, teacher_K)    权重: 渐进&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;11. SelfDistill:&lt;br&gt;    teacher 预测 → student 预测蒸馏              权重: config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;" link="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Code Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Anonymous Pro&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Droid Sans Mono&amp;quot;, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;═══ 优化损失 (losses[&quot;opt&quot;]) ═══&#xa;&#xa;1. SILog (主深度损失):&#xa;   d = log(pred_depth) - log(gt_depth)&#xa;   SILog = mean(d²) - λ × mean(d)²        权重: config&#xa;&#xa;2. depth_pre_auto:&#xa;   BinsHead 粗深度 × rays_z vs GT          权重: 0.5 × SILog.weight&#xa;&#xa;3. depth_post_auto:&#xa;   RefineModule 精深度 × rays_z vs GT      权重: 1.0 × SILog.weight&#xa;&#xa;4. dff_aux_depth:&#xa;   exp(dff_logdepth_aux) → 下采样GT比较     权重: 0.3 × SILog.weight&#xa;&#xa;5. EdgeGuidedLocalSSI:&#xa;   边缘引导局部尺度-位移不变性损失            权重: config&#xa;&#xa;6. Regression:&#xa;   L1 距离                                  权重: config&#xa;&#xa;7. Confidence_conf:&#xa;   -log(confidence) × |depth_error|          权重: config&#xa;&#xa;8. teacher_camera:&#xa;   teacher_rays vs GT rays                  权重: camera.weight&#xa;&#xa;9. distill_rays:&#xa;   warmup × 0.5 × (1 - cos(student, teacher))  权重: 渐进&#xa;&#xa;10. distill_intrinsics:&#xa;    warmup × 0.1 × MSE(student_K, teacher_K)    权重: 渐进&#xa;&#xa;11. SelfDistill:&#xa;    teacher 预测 → student 预测蒸馏              权重: config&lt;/span&gt;" id="srfS4grJ1zUWjvvm8V-F-18">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="610" width="560" x="1590" y="1707.34" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <mxCell id="srfS4grJ1zUWjvvm8V-F-19" edge="1" parent="1" style="endArrow=classic;html=1;rounded=0;" value="">
          <mxGeometry height="50" relative="1" width="50" as="geometry">
            <mxPoint x="240" y="1570" as="sourcePoint" />
            <mxPoint x="430" y="1570" as="targetPoint" />
          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Q6Midj9t3NJTiBIzXE4n-3" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Droid Sans Mono&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;      - 纹理丰富区域: RGB 已提供足够线索, 不需要焦距补充&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Droid Sans Mono&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;      - 无纹理平面(白墙/桌面): RGB 无法判断深度, 焦距信息最有价值&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Droid Sans Mono&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;      - 反光/透明物体: 深度估计最不确定, 焦距线索最需要&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Droid Sans Mono&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;      &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;- gate 零初始化 → 训练初期完全不影响主路径&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Droid Sans Mono&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: pre; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; line-height: 19px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;      - uncertainty 由 feature_map 生成 → 模型自己学什么区域需要焦距信息&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; background-color: light-dark(#ffffff, var(--ge-dark-color, #121212));&quot;&gt;      - proj 通过两层卷积对齐 focal 特征&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="130" width="560" x="1550" y="1577.34" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
